		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Once you disable the lockout chip in NES, there will still be some games that don't work... only difference left is 50/60 difference. Or there's more than that ?
<br />I have a PAL NES, and I'd like to know what NTSC games won't work on it after the lockout chip disable mod.
<br />
<br />Also, is there a simple(like SMS, MD for example) 50/60 mod for NES ? My Famicom clones have 50/60 jumpers on board...

		

