	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />All games will "work", exept maybe a few homebrew demoes that does the NTSC/PAL check and lock if it's the wrong speed. Altrough many of commercial games would have glitches in graphics as a result of improper speed. Use the ROM in an accurate emulator like Nintedulator or Nestopia set in PAL mode to predict the result before getting the cartridge.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


